  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK859">
<l>ikalkāṇā ṉākkam varuṅkā lataṉai</l>
<l>mikalkāṇuṅ kēṭu taraṟku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>At the approach of wealth one will not think of hatred (but) to secure one's ruin, one will look to its increase.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
